title: Day Trade with Tony
description:
Tony had been a senior figurehead in the technology industry for over 20 years. A keen analytical background with an engineering education meant he had a good aptitude for the financial markets. Tony, like many people of the time found himself without a position during the Covid Pandemic and as such decided to submerse himself in the world of the stock market and day trading specifically. At first, as with most day traders, Tony consistently lost a substantial amount of money in the markets until he began trading with a disciplined strategy. This strategy was borne from pattern recognition within technical analysis of stock market charting techniques and an emphasis on risk management. Tony has since been consistently profitable with this strategy having made high 6-figure gains in 2021 and multiple 7-figures in 2022 & 2023.
Tony now showcases his trading live each day sharing the knowledge and strategies he has gained since becoming a professional stock market Day Trader
